        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2020-12-01 08:28:16.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nJust had a look at JJB and it's not common to setup INFO verify job for branches other than master. And the gerrit-info-yaml-verify job doesn't support multiple branches. We might need someone with super powers here to override VBJ flag and merge in.",
        "patchset_number": 2
      },
